{"source":"recTmTnXNUPGKLCqs","target":"recT5VXFTSilSlzVX","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recTmTnXNUPGKLCqs","target":"recRxBBePxyyV6TFO","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recTmTnXNUPGKLCqs","target":"rec2Vbu9LcbJesuS0","label":"event"}],"verses":[{"id":"recGfn7GjFzoZhbMc","ref":"Gen.44.1","text":"And he commanded the steward of his house, saying, Fill the men’s sacks with food, as much as they can carry, and put every man’s money in his sack’s mouth.","year":-1707},{"id":"recIvgSOGfQfy7Ix8","ref":"Gen.44.2","text":"And put my cup, the silver cup, in the sack’s mouth of the youngest, and his corn money. And he did according to the word that Joseph had spoken.","year":-1707},{"id":"rec5gnqOCz6HLkRUl","ref":"Gen.44.3","text":"As soon as the morning was light, the men were sent away, they and their asses.","year":-1707},{"id":"recwYpg3aPBrscjoA","ref":"Gen.44.4","text":"And when they were gone out of the city, and not yet far off, Joseph said unto his steward, Up, follow after the men; and when thou dost overtake them, say unto them, Wherefore have ye rewarded evil for good?","year":-1707},{"id":"recHiuXxlKTTqEruy","ref":"Gen.44.5","text":"Is not this it in which my lord drinketh, and whereby indeed he divineth? ye have done evil in so doing.","year":-1707},{"id":"rechwt9m8hi1qSWU8","ref":"Gen.44.6","text":"And he overtook them, and he spake unto them these same words.","year":-1707},{"id":"reczmQPe720C7Ft0s","ref":"Gen.44.7","text":"And they said unto him, Wherefore saith my lord these words? God forbid that thy servants should do according to this thing:","year":-1707},{"id":"recyBobH8SVFo6ST5","ref":"Gen.44.8","text":"Behold, the money, which we found in our sacks’ mouths, we brought again unto thee out of the land of Canaan: how then should we steal out of thy lord’s house silver or gold?","year":-1707}]}
